lead_paragraph: Padraig Harrington describes 2015 with words like "grind" and "tough." It was not what he would refer to as a great year, and it doesn't sound like someone who is part of the most elite PGA Tour event of the year at Kapalua.

headline.print_headline: Padraig Harrington Has His Own Definition of a Good Year
